title: 'Curb Your Enthusiasm' Season 11 Episode 2 Recap
description:
Bill Simmons is joined by Joe House to discuss Season 11 Episode 2 of ‘Curb Your Enthusiasm.’ They talk about their favorite scenes, the funniest bits, their cast and non-cast MVPs, and grade the episode.

Hosts: Bill Simmons and Joe House
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
